	<Title>
		Glucosamine: Does it protect cartilage in osteoarthritis?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Glucosamine manufacturers claim their product slows or stops cartilage damage in osteoarthritis.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Can glucosamine supplements protect my knee cartilage from osteoarthritis?
	</Question>
